  <brief_title>Far Infrared Radiation Treatment for Osteoarthritis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 1 Study to Determine the Efficacy of Using Energy Specific Far Infrared (FIR) Radiation for the Treatment of Arthritis and Other Related Diseases</official_title>
